Package: utilsRtools
Type: Package
Title: Epigenomics NGS Data Analysis with R.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Andrea Lauria
Maintainer: The package maintainer <andrea.lauria104@gmail.com>
Description: A Collection of Tools for Next-Generation Sequencing Data Analysis, with a focus on Epigenomics research.
